<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.10.1">
<l>tīta ṟunilatto ṭerikāli ṉoṭunīrkke ḻuvicumpu mavaiyāy</l>
<l>māca ṟumaṉatti ṉoṭuṟakka moṭiṟakkai yavaiyāya perumāṉ</l>
<l>tāyce ṟavuḷaintu tayiruṇṭu kuṭamāṭu taṭamārvar takaicēr</l>
<l>nāta ṉuṟaikiṉṟa nakarnanti puraviṇṇa karamnaṇṇu maṉamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O heart, go to Nantipura Viṇṇakaram, the city where dwells</l>
<l rend="indent">the merciful lord,</l>
<l>The one with a broad chest who danced with pots,</l>
<l rend="indent">having suffered as his mother raged, [after] having eaten curds</l>
<l>Our great lord who became these: death along with a flawless heart</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] along with sleep,</l>
<l>Being [also] those: fire along with the faultless earth, water along with wind,</l>
<l rend="indent">and the brilliant heavens.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
